contactDirict_desc: We offer an integrated platform that enables you to communicate directly and instantly with a select group of lawyers specializing in various legal fields. You can request immediate legal advice via chat, schedule consultation sessions, follow up on your cases with a specialized lawyer, and securely exchange legal documents and files.
Hiring_desc: We provide you with an advanced tool to search for the lawyers best suited to your legal needs. You can search by legal specialization (criminal, commercial, family, etc.), filter results by experience and ratings, compare lawyer profiles and choose the most suitable, view reviews from previous clients, and verify lawyers' certificates and qualifications.
track_desc: An integrated system for tracking your case's progress step by step, with real-time updates on each stage, notifications of hearing dates and required tasks, central storage for all case documents, and the ability to communicate with the legal support team.
